===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-reg}}

#A [[phrase]] in which the [[initial]] (usually [[consonantal]]) sounds of two or more of the main words are [[accidentally]] [[transpose]]d.
#:''The spoonerism "The queer old dean" (instead of "the dear old Queen") is attributed to Rev. Spooner.''

